title: A Lot Like Lola
description: Lola wants everyone to be more like her until they all start acting exactly like her.

title: The Great Race
description: Elly and Pocoyo have a race, and are surprised when an outsider narrowly beats them.

title: Makes Cookies/Not Afraid Anymore/Hates Vegetables/All Alone/Tidies His Toys
description: Caillou is having fun being noisy./Caillou is afraid of Mr. Hinkle, the kind neighbor./Caillou really hates vegetables./Mom is very busy with chores and doesn't have time to play with Caillou./Caillou has left his toys all over the place.

title: Keep Going Pocoyo
description: Pato and Elly are enjoying skipping with a skipping rope. Pocoyo thinks it looks like fun and he wants to skip too. Try as he might though, Pocoyo can't do it. So he asks his friends for help.

title: Things That Go Bugs in the Night
description: Bugs must find the courage to discover what's making scary noises outside.

title: Who's Eating Mushton
description: Everyone in Mushton is finding that their precious wooden things are being munched and destroyed by someone or something. All the evidence points toward Truff's new woodworm pet Chompski. But Truff refuses to believe Chompski would do such a thing! It's up to Chep, Lilit and Mush-Mush to convince Truff. But first they have to catch Chompski in the act!

title: Twinkle Twinkle
description: Elly finds a beautiful star that has fallen out of the night sky. She loves it and wants to keep it for herself. But Pocoyo makes her realize that the star is for everyone to enjoy. Together they put it back where it's meant to be.

title: Birthday Present/Gilbert/Summer Goodnight/Scared of Dogs/The Zoo
description: It's Caillou's birthday and he's having a little party./Caillou has nobody to play with./Caillou just can't get to sleep./Caillou is scared by a stranger's dog./Caillou and his family go to the zoo.

title: Lost
description: Bing and Flop are in the park with Hoppity. What will happen when Bing finds some dog poo?

title: Fool the Forest
description: It's Fool The Forest Day when Mushables pull pranks, and MM has an epic one planned. But they spill Chanterelle's painting dye and instead must replace it by finding a rare Sloof beetle and milking it for its dye in front of everyone. Wait a minute! You can't milk a beetle! They've been pranked!

title: Caillou's Big Slide/Caillou Walks a Dog/Caillou Watches Rosie/Caillou Gets Sick/Caillou's Phone Call
description: Caillou is playing in the park with Clementine./Grandma is looking after her friend's dog again./Mommy isn't feeling well./Caillou has a fever./Mom is busy on the phone all morning.

title: Star Light, Star Bright/All in a Day's Work/The Cat's Meow/Caillou in Space
description: Caillou and the family are at Grandma & Grandpa's for an evening corn roast./The house wakes up late, and that means it's a mad rush to get off to work and off to childcare./It's time for Gilbert's annual visit to the Vet./When Caillou plays astronauts with Leo he upsets Rosie.

title: License to Deliver
description: When Percy has to deliver a new light bulb to the lighthouse at night, Thomas suggests playing secret agents along the way to help Percy forget about his fear of the dark.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The Big Sneeze
description: Elly has a cold and her huge trumpeting sneezes keep knocking Pocoyo's tower of bricks down. Pocoyo and Pato have to work out what to do.

title: Looks for Gilbert/Surprise Breakfast/Missing Sock/Goes to Work/Quarrel
description: Caillou is having a game of dinosaur hunter with Gilbert the cat./Caillou gets up early one morning./Caillou wants to wear his favorite socks, but one of them is missing./Caillou goes to work with Mom./Clementine comes over to play.

title: Like a Duck to Water
description: Daffy overcomes his fear of the swimming pool.

title: The Creature from the Chocolate Chip
description: Sylvester eats all of Granny's cookies then makes up a cookie monster to blame.

title: Christmas in July
description: The babies pretend it's Christmas in hopes of getting Lola the stethoscope she wants.

title: Magical Watering Can
description: Pocoyo gives the last drop of water from his watering can to his friends instead of using it to water his musical flowers. Pato and Elly are grateful, so they re-pay the favor.

title: The Beach/New Shoes/Snowman/Clown/Special Friend
description: Caillou and his family are at the beach./Caillou gets a new pair of shoes./Caillou wants to make a snowman./Caillou is going to a parade with horses, drummers and clowns./Caillou's having fun with his friend.

title: Daycare/Joins the Circus/Afraid of the Dark/Friends/Visits the Doctor
description: It's Caillou's first day at daycare and he doesn't want to go./Caillou gets dressed all by himself./Caillou can't get to sleep./Caillou is talking to Grandma. She's surprised./Caillou has an ear infection.

title: Shadow
description: Bing is playing shadow tag with Flop, but what will happen when the clouds come?

title: Let It Bee
description: Wanting to rush off to climb Mush Mountain, Mush-Mush is in a hurry checking nectar level in flowers - a job that takes time and care. Soon Mush-Mush's haste causes disaster when he scares all the bees away. Now Mush-Mush and friends have to find a way to lure the bees back…

title: Big Jumping Spider
description: When Findley comments to Lucas that his jump isn't very long or high Lucas ramps things up, jumping higher and longer in ever increasing death defying jumps. Findley is now beginning to regret his comment and wishes Lucas wouldn't jump so far. This all culminates in Lucas going for the big one in his car down a track. Can Findley convince him not too?

title: A Secret Tweet
description: The babies plan a surprise birthday party for Tweety.

title: Mother's Day Madness
description: The babies compete to see who can create the best Mother's Day card.

title: Frog
description: Bing and Sula find a frog in the garden, but will Froggy like her new bucket house?

title: Parking Lot
description: Bing's parking his speedy cars but what will Bing do when Charlie wants to play too?

title: Race the Beast
description: Mush-Mush and his friends are determined to win the bark sledge race, but their essential fourth team member drops out. Our friends ask Mushpot to step up from being their coach to racing with them. The Mushelder is reluctant at first but soon reveals the tough competitor he is!

title: Fetch Loula Fetch!
description: Pocoyo and Loula are going to the beach, but they keep losing their ball. They learn about colors, shapes and sizes as they meet their friends along the way.

title: A Mystery Most Puzzling
description: Pocoyo has to follow the clues in a series of photographs to work out who's got the camera.

title: Let's Go Camping!
description: A camping trip is planned - but Pocoyo and Pato have too much luggage. In the end they realize that all you really need for a nice camping trip are your friends - and then it doesn't really matter whether you're at home or away.

title: Save the Fun Tree
description: Mush-Mush and friends' favorite play tree, the Fun Tree, is rotten and doomed. But Mush-Mush refuses to give up on it. In a last ditch effort to save the tree, our friends adventure off to try and track down the legendary Starmush, hoping his mysterious healing powers can save it.

title: The Snake Dance
description: When Mush-Mush and Chep lose Lilit's flying disc down a snake tunnel, he is confident he can get it back. All animals love Chep and no one knows more about snakes than he does. But this snake is not to be messed with! When they finally sneak into the snake tunnel, they learn why the snake has been acting so strangely…

title: Where's Pocoyo?
description: Pocoyo plays hide and seek with us. Can you find him?

title: Bat and Ball
description: It's time for a game of Bat and Ball with Octopus. Everyone wants to have a turn at batting, but the friends learn that you have to wait your turn.

title: Shadow of a Doubt
description: Tweety sheds some light on what a shadow is.

title: A Little Cloud
description: Pocoyo has an unusual new friend: a lonely little cloud who just wants to play.

title: Swept Away
description: Pocoyo shows us that tidying can be fun too: a broom can be a horse, a guitar, or even a hockey stick!

title: My Muddy Buddy
description: When Lilit creates a 'friends tree' mapping out who everyone is best friends with in Mushton, she realizes Muddler has no friends at all. Unable to accept this, Lilit slips away to try and befriend him. But Muddler's perception of friendship is somewhat unique, meaning Lilit now needs the help of her two best friends, Mush-Mush and Chep, to escape from Muddler's clutches.

title: Grasshopper Chep
description: All the Mushables have fun zooming down a long mudslide except Chep, who just can't get up the courage to do it. But when Fung and Miff tease him for being scared, he promises that he will do something that no Mushable has ever done before - ride a grasshopper! Chep is in for the ride of his life!

title: Card Bored Box
description: Faced with nothing to do, the babies use a cardboard box and their imaginations to make playtime fun.

title: Fireworks
description: Bing is excited to watch the Fireworks outside, but will they be too noisy?

title: A Present for Elly
description: Pocoyo decides to make a very special birthday present for Elly. Can you guess what it is?

title: Hush
description: Pocoyo and his gang want to make friends with a butterfly but every time they say hello, it flies away. With Sleepy Bird's help, they realize how to get close to the butterfly.

title: Drummer Boy
description: Pocoyo wants to drum, but his friends are all busy playing different things. Pocoyo learns that sometimes his friends don't want to do exactly the same things as him.

title: Unlock the Magic: The Beginning
description: The discovery of an ancient, lost gateway leads the Care Bears on a rescue mission in the Silver Lining, a realm of natural wonders and comical creatures in the clouds beyond the borders of Care-A-Lot. While there, new discoveries expand the mission, challenging Cheer, Grumpy, and the mission team to grow beyond their present abilities and help the denizens of the Silver Lining.

title: The Biggest Adventure Club
description: When Thomas finds a treasure map he creates "The Big Adventure Club," to seek the treasure, but when Sandy wants to join, Thomas says she's too little, so Sandy forms her own club.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Cat-Taz-Trophy
description: Sylvester and Taz team up to win a toy racecar derby.

title: Here I Go
description: Bing and Pando find a new slide at the playground, but it's very high. Will Bing be able to go down the slide?

title: Having a Ball
description: Pocoyo and Pato are enjoying playing with their new ball. But all of a sudden, the ball takes on a life of its own, and Pocoyo and Pato have to chase it. Who's got the ball…? It's Baby Bird who just wants to play too!

title: Snails Forever
description: Chep wants to return a favor to Mush-Mush, but all Mush-Mush wants is to have a compost pancake on Pancake Day! But when the Food Snail falls for, and takes off after, the Travel Snail, Pancake Day has to be cancelled. Chep sees an opportunity to save the day for his friend! But er, how do you solve a snail falling for another?

title: The Hero Trap
description: The Mushlets love Mush-Mush's heroic stories. But when they demand to see him actually do something heroic, Mush-Mush feels he can't back out - and so ends up stuck up a cliff. Relieved to be rescued by Chep and Lilit, Mush-Mush is about to admit that he isn't a hero when the Mushlets find themselves in danger. Now Mush-Mush has no choice but to be a real hero!

title: Pato's Postal Service
description: When Pocoyo wants to send a letter to Elly, Pato embraces the very important role of postman. After much to-ing and fro-ing, Pato delivers a mammoth package!

title: Fussy Duck
description: Pato, fresh from his shower, is determined to keep clean. Pocoyo and Elly have very different ideas, and Pato soon realizes that half the fun of getting clean is getting dirty in the first place!

title: Musical Statues
description: Bing gets to choose the game at Amma's Creche, but will his also be the winner?

title: Bird Call
description: Chanterelle has built a whistle that can reproduce the most beautiful sound of the forest: the one of the Nightingale. When the whistle disappears, Mush-Mush, Chep and Lilit soon discover that it has been stolen by a beetle. In order to finally hear what a real Nightingale sounds like, they'll have to get it back!

title: Too Hot to Handle
description: Findley can't resist some freshly baked cookies that are too hot to eat so Lucas and his friends do whatever it takes to keep him from burning his mouth.

title: Smoothie
description: It's snack time, but what will Bing and Flop make with the mushy banana?

title: Time and Time Again
description: The babies learn the importance of telling time.

title: Plays Baby/Flies on a Plane/In the Bathtub/Goes Birdwatching/The Doll
description: Caillou thinks his sister Rosie is getting favorable treatment./It's Caillou's first flight./It's bathtime, and for Caillou that means trouble./Grandma always has the best surprises./Mom is putting on her makeup to go out with Dad.

title: Voo Voo
description: It's breakfast time, and when Bing accidentally spills his Krispos, Voo Voo can help clean it up. But will that be all Voo Voo cleans up?

title: Oh My Compost
description: When Sushi-Mushi breaks the only spoon he has ever cooked with, he declares his cooking days are over! So Mush-Mush and friends step up to cook for everyone instead. How hard can it be? It turns out, very! The Mushlers will have to convince Sushi-Mushi he's still the best compost chef, even without his favorite spoon!

title: The Missing Mushlet
description: So Mushpie can take a break, Mush-Mush, Chep and Lilit offer to look after the Mushies, assuring her that everything will be fine. But a Mushie pops to become a Mushlet and escapes. Our friends find him in Muddler's clutches! Now, they must figure out a way to save the Mushlet and return the other Mushies to their cave before the return of Mushpie.

title: Puppy Love
description: Pocoyo neglects Loula when he finds a toy dog to play with.

title: Learns to Drive/Big Friend/Colors/Mails a Letter/Learns to Swim
description: Caillou loves anything to do with cars./Caillou meets a new friend called André./Caillou visits Grandma's house./Mom is upset when the mailman only brings bills./Caillou goes to the swimming pool with his family and Daddy teaches him how to swim.

title: Comfort Level
description: Sylvester learns to live without his blankey.

title: School Daze
description: The babies play pretend school in preparation for the real thing.

title: Takers Keepers
description: Daffy steals Taz's favorite toy but he learns you can't just take everything you want.

title: Percy's Lucky Bell
description: When Thomas borrows Percy's lucky bell for a dangerous delivery, Thomas isn't careful and loses the bell.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Suprise, It's Spring
description: Puff doesn't like change much. And with spring about to burst forth and all the changes spring brings, he is puffing out nervous fog which is blanketing the whole of Mushton. Mush-Mush and friends need to get Puff to relax and celebrate spring together with all the other Mushables!

title: Umbrella, Umbrella
description: Pocoyo finds an umbrella. He and his friends have great fun playing with the umbrella and trying to work out what it's for. When it starts to rain, Pocoyo - with the help of the children watching - realizes a perfect use for it!

title: Atchoo
description: Bing is so excited to see Sula and eat some of Amma's carroty bagels, but what will happen when he can't stop sneezing and feels all hot?

title: Mushlers to the Rescue
description: Having rescued a Mushlet, Mush-Mush, Chep and Lilit become heroes in Mushton, and they're loving it! So Mushlers create a rescue team but alas, no one needs saving! How can you be a hero when there is nothing to be heroic about? Then when some Mushlets become adrift on the river, Team Mush-Mush, with Morel's help, have to save the day again.

title: Train
description: Bing's train can do lots of great things in the park's playground, but as Bing and Pando climb higher, what else will the train do?

title: Blocks
description: Bing is building a tower with his blocks but what will happen when both he and Coco want the last red block?

title: Stuck in the Mud
description: When Fung and Miff spoil Mush-Mush's fun tunnel surprise he has been working on for ages, he wishes their day was ruined too. And then it is, because they are taken by Muddler! Now our Mushlers have to go on a rescue mission to save Fung and Miff.

title: Juggling Balls
description: Pocoyo is very impressed with Elly and Octopus' trick of juggling. He wants to play too. Octopus makes Pocoyo practice lots of different activities but Pocoyo can't see the point because they aren't related to juggling… or so he thinks. In the end Pocoyo becomes the star of the show!

title: Growing
description: Bing is having his height measured by Flop, but what will happen when Coco measures him again?

title: Bake
description: Bing and Flop are baking Ginger Bunny cookies in the oven for Coco and Charlie. Will Chickie Timer ring to tell them it's time to come out of the oven?

title: Ducks
description: Bing and Sula are feeding the ducks in the park, but will Bing remember to stand statue still?

title: Swing
description: Bing and Pando are taking turns on the swing. Bing counts to ten, but will Pando do the same?

title: May the Best Taz Win
description: Lola learns she can't be the best at every sport.

title: Goes Camping/Learns to Skate/Gets Dressed/Daddy/Grows Carrots
description: Caillou hears about Daddy's first camping trip./Caillou has a hard time skating./Mom's doing the laundry./Mom and Rosie are out for the day. Caillou and Dad will spend the day together./Grandpa helps Mom make a vegetable garden.

title: Say Goodbye
description: Bing and Sula are having so much fun playing together, they don't want to say goodbye. What will happen when Amma comes to collect Sula?

title: Duck! Monster! Duck!
description: Daffy reads the babies a scary story, only to end up frightening himself.

title: Taz in Toyland
description: After Taz breaks all of his toys, Granny gives him one last chance to care for something.

title: The Staff of Wisdom
description: Mush-Mush is amazed by the way Mushpot uses his staff of wisdom and how awesome it makes him look. Mush-Mush wants to be as cool as Mushpot and asks him to lend him his staff of wisdom. But the staff comes with a lot of responsibilities.

title: Pocoyo, Pocoyo
description: Pocoyo discovers a fabulous new playmate - his echoooo-ooo-ooo-ooo!

title: Sylvester the Pester
description: An attention-starved Sylvester won't let Granny have any time to herself.

title: A Frog of a Problem
description: MM's favorite frog has had its home taken over by a lizard. Mushpot says not to interfere, nature must run its course. But Lilit feels so sorry for the frog she takes it back to Mushton where it causes havoc. Now our friends must lure the frog back to its home where it deals with the lizard itself.

title: New Babysitter/Theme Park/School Bus/Sleeps Over/Hurts Himself
description: Mom and Dad are going out./Caillou and his family go to a theme park./Caillou doesn't go to school./It's the first time Caillou is going to spend the night away from his home./Poor Caillou! He's fallen off his bike and scraped his knee.

title: The Key to it All
description: Pocoyo finds a key which leads him on an exciting and magical adventure of exploration and discovery.

title: Hide & Seek
description: Bing's friends all catch the toilet train before playing hide-and-seek but Bing doesn't need to go. Will Bing need the toilet before the game ends?

title: Pocoyo Gets it Right
description: Pocoyo wants to play 'pitch and putt' like his friends, Pocoyo and Elly, but he can't quite get the hang of it. He watches carefully and finally grasps where he was going wrong.

title: Rules of the Game
description: When Thomas builds an obstacle course for his friends, he gets upset when they won't play with it HIS way.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Pocoyo Dance
description: Pocoyo finds a radio. Pato does his funny, funky dance and Elly demonstrates her delicate ballet style. Pocoyo hears a tune he likes and finds his groove. Everyone can dance in their own special way!

title: Spin Out
description: Taz learns a tough lesson. He shouldn't spin after eating too much candy.

title: The Big Squeak
description: Avocado's new toy is driving everyone crazy with its noisy squeaker. Lucas tells everyone that he's going to speak to her and realizes Avocado loves everything about her squeaky toy apart from the actual squeak itself! So, Dr. Lucas is in the house to operate and remove the squeak.

title: Mine!
description: Daffy learns a lesson in doing the right thing when he finds a purse filled with money.

title: Caillou Beats the Heat/Back Seat Driver/Lost and Found/Holiday Magic
description: It's hot and steamy and Mom won't let Caillou go to the public pool./Caillou, Dad and Rosie are in the car on their way to meet Mom./When Dad and Caillou find a scruffy dog that appears to be lost they bring it home./Caillou and his family pay a visit to Santa and go Christmas tree shopping all in the same day.

title: Fly, Chase, Fly
description: Chep is disappointed Mush-Mush and Lilit are too busy leaf-gliding to play moss-ball with him, so he hangs out with a new weevil friend instead. But Chep's new friend must migrate with all the other weevils. Except he doesn't know how to fly! Chep must teach him to fly while overcoming his own secret fear of heights.

title: The Brave Little Tweety
description: Tweety takes a role in a play too seriously and begins to believe he's a real superhero.

title: Bye Bye
description: Bing loves playing with his new orange balloon, but what will happen when he bounces on it too much?

title: Snow Day
description: The babies experience their first snowfall.

title: Up Up and Away
description: Our friends are playing with a model airplane which shoots off up into space. They go on an adventure to retrieve the beloved toy, encountering some friendly, bendy aliens along the way.

title: Elly Spots
description: Elly is stricken with a case of the Elly Spots, and Pato and Pocoyo have to forsake their picnic to look after her. Once she is better, she makes it up to them.

title: Get the Egg Home
description: When an egg blows down into the village, it is Mush-Mush and friends' mission to return it to Mush Mountain. Two problems though: there is a Beetle Boom on and all the beetles try to charge and knock over Mushables, and Lilit has always wanted to see an egg hatch so secretly drags her feet.

title: Big Brother/Hiding Place/Rainy Day/Rakes the Leaves/Goes Shopping
description: Caillou remembers when he first met his sister./Caillou is at his Grandparents' house./It's a rainy day and Caillou wants to jump in all the puddles./Caillou and Rosie have so much fun playing in the leaves./Caillou is looking forward to making a snowman.

title: To Tell the Tooth
description: When Bugs loses a baby tooth, Daffy tries to figure out how to scam the tooth fairy.

title: Puddle Olympics
description: The kids take turns jumping over a puddle but Sylvester is afraid of the water.
